\id PHM - Misima [MPX September, 1997; backslash codes updated: 21-Aug-2006]
\h PILIMON
\toc3 Pilm
\toc2 Pilimon
\toc1 Pilimon wana Leta
\mt1 Pilimon wana Leta
\mt2 Pol wana Leleli
\is1 Baaba Houwan
\ip Pilimon iya Kolose gamagalina ge iya toabulilek. Wana totuwalali loloyowanina etega alana Onisimo, yaa Onisimo wana tonowak i lou luwai. Tabam wana tonowak wana mani enuna i kaome al iyaka i lou (puna 18). Sauga i lou, i na panuwa Loma, ge abwe Pol i pwawaa to. Inoke Pol wana liwaliwan eliyana Onisimo i tabwa toabulilek (puna 10).
\ip Pol nuwana Onisimo ni patuna ni sikal Pilimon elana. Yaa Loma wali logugui i ba bosowaina Pilimon ni ba tolohaveyan Onisimo nihi lopaaliga, o ebo ana lahi enuna al ni baunan, kaiwena i lou luwai. Inoke Pol Pilimon wana leta ya i ginol ge i awanun Pilimon alona wana nunuwana Onisimo ni ahe pasikal (puna 16 ge 17).
\ip He ana awa i ola Pol leta toto ya ge Kolose wali leta i ginol sauga maisena elana ge i patuna pamaisena (Kolose 4:9).
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Nau Pol, he Keliso Yeisu kaiwena ya minaa dela. Alou ge talila Timoti leta ya ha ginol ge ha patuna i nowa Pilimon eliyam, owa wama heliyam nunuwanina ge wama pan totuwalali,
\v 2 alomwau ge toekelesiya bolo hi mimigogowa wam limiya. I ola al, ha patuna numa Apiya eliyam, ge Akipas eliyam, owa wama pan tolohaveyan Keliso kaiwena.
\p 
\v 3 Ha awanun Yehoba Tamala ge Babala Yeisu Keliso nihi muloluagimiu ge wali nuwa laumwal atemiu ni pakalaopop.
\s1 Pilimon wana Abulilek ge wana Nunuwana
\p 
\v 4 Sauga gegewena no awanun elana ya awaawanun Pilimon kaiwem ge ya babaa mulolu no Yabowaine elana,
\v 5 kaiwena wasam ya hago te wam abulilek i gasisi Babala Yeisu elana ge wam nunuwana i bwata Yehoba wana gamagalau gegewel elal.
\v 6 Wam abulilek kaiwena iyaka alomwau ge Yehoba wana gamagalau ku heliheliyam, inoke ya awanun Yehoba elana heliheliyam o paganina ni gagasisi eliyam, kaiwena waisi gegewena toto Keliso eliyana i gan elala u atena.
\v 7 Taliu, Yehoba wana gamagalau u nunuwana-agil ge ateliya u payaliyaya, inoke wam ginol o i payaliyaya-agau ge i pagasisi-agau.
\s1 Pol I Awanun Pilimon elana Onisimo kaiwena
\p 
\v 8 Bugul etega nuwau te binimala nu ginol, ge bosowaiu Keliso alana elana na ba ge nu ginol,
\v 9 yaa owa ge nau wala penunuwana kaiwena nasi na awanun ya elam. Nau Pol, iyaka ya tonowak ge Keliso Yeisu kaiwena ya minaa dela,
\v 10 ya awanun elam nuwau nu ginol bubun natu Onisimo elana. Sauga nau iyahe ya miminaa dela, i nem elau ya labe ge i tabwa toabulilek, inoke ya awa natuni.
\v 11 Valila iya nige wam totuwalali waiwaisana i oola, yaa sauga ya iyaka i tabwa owa ge nau wala totuwalali waiwaisana.\f * \fr 1:11 \ft Pana Gilik elana alan Onisimo ana sapu i gan, heiya te “tolaba waiwaisana.”\f*
\p 
\v 12 Iya ateu nunuwanina te ya papatuna pasikal elam e.
\v 13 He no nuwatu te binimala na kukuhikan, inoke sauga nau iyahe ya minamina dela Wasa Waiwaisana ana tuwalali kaiwena, abam ni ahe ge ni tuwalali o labe kaiwena.
\v 14 Yaa nige ya kukuhikan, kaiwena nige nuwau bugul etega na ginol ebo nige u aatena ge u tatalam. Nige nuwau o labe kaiwena ge na palawakikiwa, yaa binimala totom wam nuwatu ge wam atitalam elana ge nu labeyau.
\v 15 He i eguluwagiwa sauga kakaubwaina ya, tabam puna heiya te ge nu ahe pasikal ni ola talim ge ni mihot elam.
\v 16 He sauga ya iya nige totuwalali loloyowanina ya i oola. Tunahot iya totuwalali loloyowanina, yaa i ola al iya talim nunuwanina Keliso elana. Ana nunuwana i bwata eliyau, yaa nasi ana nunuwana ni bwata hot eliyam, iya wam totuwalali ge iya talim Babala elana.
\p 
\v 17 Ebo nu atena nau wam pan totuwalali, alom ge wam yaliyaya nu ahe pasikal ni ola te ebo nau u aaheyau.
\v 18 Ebo valila bugul etega i ginol panak elam, o ebo ana vaga i gan elam, he vaga o nu teliya alawa.
\v 19 Sauga ya nau Pol totou nimwau elana ya leleli:\f * \fr 1:19 \ft Ana awa i ola leta ya ana baaba Pol i baunan ge gamagal getoga i leli lowan. Yaa puna 19 ge i nok Pol totona nimana elana i leleli.\f* nau vaga o na pwamola pasikal. (He owa al am vaga i gan elau, yawalim ana pwamwal vagana. Yaa nige nuwau na baaba bugul o kaiwena.)
\v 20 Taliu, ya awanun Babala alana elana nu labeyau nu ginol ni ola to. He kila ta minaa Keliso elana, inoke no awanun nu hago ge ateu nu payaliyaya.
\v 21 Ateu i matuwa te nasi nu ginol ni ola no baaba, inoke ya leli i ola to. He ya atena wam ginol Onisimo elana nasi ni waisi hot ge toto ya awanuni ni waisi lake.
\p 
\v 22 Ge bugul etega al: abakenu etega nu lovivina-an kaiweu, kaiwena ya abulilek te wami awanun Yehoba ni hago ge ni pasikalau na nowa eliyamiu.
\s1 Lokaiyoni
\p 
\v 23 Epapilas, iya iyahe Keliso Yeisu kaiwena alou ha minamina dela, i mulolu eliyam.
\v 24 I ola al, Mak, Alistako, Dimasa ge Luke, heliya no pan totuwalali, hi mulolu eliyam.
\p 
\v 25 Babala Yeisu Keliso wana mulolu ni minaa ku gewigewi eliyamiu. 
